### Get all notes
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notes
Accept: application/json

###

### Get note by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notes/1
Accept: application/json

###

### Create a new note
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notes
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "My new note",
  "content": "This is a sample note created for testing.",
  "comment": "Random comment"
}

###

### Create note without title (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notes
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "content": "Missing title test"
}

###

### Create note without content (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notes
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "title": "Missing content test"
}

###

### Get non-existing note (should return 404)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notes/9999
Accept: application/json

###

### Healthcheck (if added to the app)
GET http://localhost:8080/health
Accept: application/json